<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-03-09T02:29:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-03-09T02:29:00-05:00" n="497" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d497">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.00/1194</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Gonzales</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-03-09T02:00:00-05:29">
                                    <hi rend="italic">March 9, 1917, 2 a.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Suggest that naval commander at Santiago have substance of President
                            Menocal’s proclamation of today posted in streets, then land battalion
                            marines, and notify rebel commander he must submit to Government or go
                            outside city to fight federal troops. This would relieve apprehension of
                            bloodshed in city and there would probably be little outside.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>